This forest of logically and emotionally exposed and branching information trees, memory registers, is used by the brain in its recognition, cognitive, process, I am exposed to a constantly changing presence, in an unceasing effort to name and understand its surroundings and decode important messages.
Sometimes overload faults occur.
Analogously - as if your PC &quot;fell down&quot;, from the speech emulator and foreign language translator program you would first get confused in the operating environment, for example Windows, and after several unsuccessful restarts you would end up at the dark green flashing Bios screen, in the basic system that controls the functions and cooperation on the motherboard, between the processor and operating memory, etc.
For those who haven&#39;t yet understood what I&#39;m talking about - I&#39;m talking about a psycho-spiritual crisis.
